metadata.name: Son of Sun
metadata.description: You might be scared of his face at first, but he is the kindest being in this galaxy, his face looks burnt due to the weather conditions of the sun. But he has a heart as warm as the sun. He fought a great battle with the devil in his star and was able to drive the devil out of the star of the sun. Now he has decided to do something great and you will get to know his story in the next episodes...
